<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Entry Not Found</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      color-scheme: light;
      font-family: "Inter", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background-color: #f7f9fc;
      color: #1a2a3a;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f9fbff 0%, #eef4fb 100%);
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 2.5rem 3rem;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(18, 48, 85, 0.12);
      max-width: 28rem;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    p {
      margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
      color: #4e6479;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a {
      color: #3556d2;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h1>Entry Missing</h1>
    <p>We could not find an entry with id <strong><%= id %></strong> in this database.</p>
    <a href="/">Back to dashboard</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
